pa-network-volume-control


Client:
cd into the client folder and make

launch with:
./pa-nvc <hostname> <port>

Binded keys:
<CTRL>+    increase volume
<CTRL>-    decrease volume
<CTRL>*    mute
<CTRL>/    unmute

+,-,*,/ are the ones the numpad

Server:
cd into the server folder and make
launch with:
./pa-nvcs <port>

Libraries:
To compile the server on a Ubuntu machine, you'll need
these packages:
 - libpulse-dev
 - build-essential
